There is one interior patch pocket to put your phone or keys in.

38 cm at widest point across bottom 
23cm tall when seated 
11cm deep 
61cm straps 


You can choose between black or green lining and trim. 
Fabric placement might slightly differ due to fabric pattern. 


*this bag was made using a keykalou pattern.
